  propMaterialOverrides: []
  introLines:
  - Oh, wow. Is the party over? Did the kid make it?
  - I am so sorry if I'm dripping water on your floor, my boots are full of it
  answerWhatHappenedBefore: A little kid bounced way too high and was flying over
    the safety wall. I dove to catch him, caught him perfectly, but cracked my head
    right on a concrete garden gnome
  answerWhatKindOfLife: Busy, kind of exhausting, but nice. I spent most of my time
    trying to make children smile and helping my aunt with her rent
  answerWhatWasYourJob: I dressed up as a bootleg spider-hero for low-budget children's
    parties. The fabric was incredibly itchy
  answerWhatHappenedClothes: I didn't even have time to change out of my work outfit.
    It's wrinkled and smells faintly of juice boxes and sweat
  answerWhyHaveItem: It's a plastic kid's colored hat from the party! I was holding
    it for the birthday boy. Can you make sure he gets it back?
